[
    {
        "text": "You've probably heard the word engineering before...",
        "startTime": 749,
        "endTime": 2954,
        "slowStartTime": 1274,
        "slowEndTime": 4656
    },
    {
        "text": "...and you've probably been told it's pretty important.",
        "startTime": 3301,
        "endTime": 5382,
        "slowStartTime": 5101,
        "slowEndTime": 8298
    },
    {
        "text": "But what exactly is engineering?",
        "startTime": 5975,
        "endTime": 7886,
        "slowStartTime": 9113,
        "slowEndTime": 12054
    },
    {
        "text": "And who exactly is an engineer?",
        "startTime": 8194,
        "endTime": 10071,
        "slowStartTime": 12441,
        "slowEndTime": 15332
    },
    {
        "text": "Engineers are people who design and build things that we use every day.",
        "startTime": 10733,
        "endTime": 13876,
        "slowStartTime": 16250,
        "slowEndTime": 21039
    },
    {
        "text": "However, they don't just go building the first thing that comes to mind.",
        "startTime": 14370,
        "endTime": 17443,
        "slowStartTime": 21705,
        "slowEndTime": 26389
    },
    {
        "text": "They work hard to make something we need and they want to do a good job of it.",
        "startTime": 17841,
        "endTime": 21419,
        "slowStartTime": 26911,
        "slowEndTime": 32354
    },
    {
        "text": "So how do engineers decide what they need to build?",
        "startTime": 21871,
        "endTime": 24115,
        "slowStartTime": 32956,
        "slowEndTime": 36398
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, in most cases, they start with a question.",
        "startTime": 24709,
        "endTime": 26815,
        "slowStartTime": 37213,
        "slowEndTime": 40448
    },
    {
        "text": "Here's an example.",
        "startTime": 27402,
        "endTime": 28167,
        "slowStartTime": 41253,
        "slowEndTime": 42476
    },
    {
        "text": "Say you live on a space station and something outside breaks.",
        "startTime": 28605,
        "endTime": 32180,
        "slowStartTime": 43057,
        "slowEndTime": 48495
    },
    {
        "text": "Obviously, you need to go outside and fix it.",
        "startTime": 32729,
        "endTime": 34708,
        "slowStartTime": 49244,
        "slowEndTime": 52287
    },
    {
        "text": "But how exactly do you do that?",
        "startTime": 35051,
        "endTime": 36993,
        "slowStartTime": 52727,
        "slowEndTime": 55714
    },
    {
        "text": "That's a great question for engineers.",
        "startTime": 37505,
        "endTime": 39349,
        "slowStartTime": 56407,
        "slowEndTime": 59248
    },
    {
        "text": "Once they've got a good handle on things, they'll start imagining ways to solve the problem.",
        "startTime": 40837,
        "endTime": 45286,
        "slowStartTime": 61405,
        "slowEndTime": 68154
    },
    {
        "text": "They'll come up with all kinds of ideas and some that might even seem a little crazy.",
        "startTime": 45882,
        "endTime": 50825,
        "slowStartTime": 68973,
        "slowEndTime": 76462
    },
    {
        "text": "That's important because sometimes the craziest idea is the one that works best.",
        "startTime": 51252,
        "endTime": 55910,
        "slowStartTime": 77028,
        "slowEndTime": 84090
    },
    {
        "text": "After coming up with these ideas, they'll pick a few that make the most sense.",
        "startTime": 56303,
        "endTime": 60241,
        "slowStartTime": 84605,
        "slowEndTime": 90586
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, they'll start drawing a plan.",
        "startTime": 61057,
        "endTime": 62757,
        "slowStartTime": 91736,
        "slowEndTime": 94360
    },
    {
        "text": "Depending on the idea, the plan can be very simple or very complicated.",
        "startTime": 63142,
        "endTime": 67955,
        "slowStartTime": 94863,
        "slowEndTime": 102158
    },
    {
        "text": "But the important part is the plan itself.",
        "startTime": 68382,
        "endTime": 70563,
        "slowStartTime": 102723,
        "slowEndTime": 106069
    },
    {
        "text": "A good plan helps engineers focus on what they're making and most importantly, why.",
        "startTime": 71144,
        "endTime": 75957,
        "slowStartTime": 106866,
        "slowEndTime": 114161
    }
]